## 📈 Recent Improvements
- **Zero Build Errors**: Project compiles successfully with `tsc && vite build`.
- **SRP Enforcement**: No more 1000-line monolithic modules.
- **Lazy Resolution**: UI components now resolve services at runtime via `container.resolve`, preventing circular dependencies.
- **Event-Driven Navigation**: Removed polling in favor of `onPageChange` subscriptions.